OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy and often damp during
OL,6,Fthis morning with spells of light rain
OL,7,Fand drizzle. Brighter breaks may occur
OL,8,Fin southern counties this afternoon
OL,9,Fbut heavy showers or longer periods of
OL,10,Frain will become increasingly likely
OL,11,Flater. Not quite as mild.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FRain or showers this evening
OL,14,Fbut turning much drier from around
OL,15,Fmidnight with clear spells developing
OL,16,Flater in the night. Turning locally
OL,17,Fchilly by dawn with isolated fog
OL,18,Fpatches possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
