OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FIsolated showers may affect
OL,6,Fnorthern counties for a time, but
OL,7,Fotherwise a fine day with a mixture of
OL,8,Fcloudy spells and sunny periods.
OL,9,FSomewhat less mild but winds generally
OL,10,Flight.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FDamp
OL,13,Fand windier on Sunday with periods of
OL,14,Fdrizzly rain, this mostly over the
OL,15,Fhills. Generally drier on Monday but
OL,16,Fshowery rain still possible. Perhaps
OL,17,Fbrighter on Tuesday. Staying mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
